              <li>HTTP protocol fundamentals</li>
              <li>RESTful API concepts</li>
              <li>SQL basics (SELECT, JOIN, INSERT)</li>
              <li>Git version control</li>
              <li>Command line/terminal</li>
              <li>Basic data structures</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
