          <div class="skill-level"><div class="skill-level-header"><span class="skill-level-badge skill-level-advanced">Advanced</span><span class="skill-level-time">24+ months</span></div><ul class="skill-level-list"><li>System architecture design</li><li>Performance optimization (both ends)</li><li>Cloud deployment (AWS/Azure)</li><li>CI/CD implementation</li><li>Microservices concepts</li><li>Security best practices</li><li>TypeScript mastery</li><li>GraphQL or similar</li></ul></div>
