    <div class="roadmap-panel" role="tabpanel" id="panel-mobile" aria-labelledby="tab-mobile" hidden>

      <div class="roadmap-intro">
        <h3>Mobile Developer</h3>
        <p class="roadmap-intro-desc">Build native and cross-platform mobile applications for iOS and Android. Create smooth, performant experiences users carry in their pockets every day.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="roadmap-block">
        <h3 class="roadmap-block-title">Role Overview &amp; Responsibilities</h3>
        <p>Mobile developers build applications for smartphones and tablets. You design user interfaces optimized for touch, integrate with device features (camera, GPS, notifications), manage app state, consume APIs, handle offline capability, and navigate app store submission processes. The role requires understanding platform-specific guidelines (Apple HIG, Material Design) and performance constraints of mobile devices.</p>
        <p>Daily work includes implementing UI screens, integrating REST APIs, debugging on physical devices, writing unit and UI tests, optimizing app performance and battery usage, handling push notifications, and keeping up with OS updates and new device capabilities.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="roadmap-block">
        <h3 class="roadmap-block-title">Required Skills: Beginner → Advanced</h3>
        <div class="skills-progression">
          <div class="skill-level"><div class="skill-level-header"><span class="skill-level-badge skill-level-beginner">Beginner</span><span class="skill-level-time">0–6 months</span></div><ul class="skill-level-list"><li>Swift (iOS) or Kotlin (Android)</li><li>Platform IDE (Xcode / Android Studio)</li><li>UI layout fundamentals</li><li>Mobile design guidelines</li><li>Git version control</li><li>Basic networking (REST API calls)</li><li>App lifecycle understanding</li></ul></div>
          <div class="skill-level"><div class="skill-level-header"><span class="skill-level-badge skill-level-intermediate">Intermediate</span><span class="skill-level-time">6–18 months</span></div><ul class="skill-level-list"><li>State management patterns</li><li>Local storage (Core Data / Room)</li><li>Push notifications</li><li>Authentication flows</li><li>Unit &amp; UI testing</li><li>Performance optimization</li><li>Cross-platform basics (React Native / Flutter)</li><li>App Store / Play Store submission</li></ul></div>
          <div class="skill-level"><div class="skill-level-header"><span class="skill-level-badge skill-level-advanced">Advanced</span><span class="skill-level-time">18+ months</span></div><ul class="skill-level-list"><li>Advanced architecture (MVVM, Clean Architecture)</li><li>Custom animations &amp; transitions</li><li>Offline-first architecture</li><li>CI/CD for mobile (Fastlane)</li><li>Accessibility on mobile</li><li>App performance profiling</li><li>SwiftUI / Jetpack Compose</li><li>Cross-platform expertise (Flutter/React Native)</li></ul></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="roadmap-block">
        <h3 class="roadmap-block-title">Technologies &amp; Learning Order</h3>
        <div class="timeline">
          <div class="timeline-item"><div class="timeline-marker" aria-hidden="true"></div><div class="timeline-content"><span class="timeline-period">Months 1–3</span><h3>Core Language &amp; IDE</h3><p>Learn Swift or Kotlin. Set up Xcode or Android Studio. Build simple apps with basic UI layouts and navigation.</p></div></div>
          <div class="timeline-item"><div class="timeline-marker" aria-hidden="true"></div><div class="timeline-content"><span class="timeline-period">Months 4–6</span><h3>UI &amp; User Experience</h3><p>Master platform UI components, auto layout / constraint layout, navigation patterns, design guidelines.</p></div></div>
          <div class="timeline-item"><div class="timeline-marker" aria-hidden="true"></div><div class="timeline-content"><span class="timeline-period">Months 7–10</span><h3>Networking &amp; Data</h3><p>REST API integration, JSON parsing, local databases, image loading, caching strategies.</p></div></div>
          <div class="timeline-item"><div class="timeline-marker" aria-hidden="true"></div><div class="timeline-content"><span class="timeline-period">Months 11–14</span><h3>Advanced Features</h3><p>Push notifications, authentication, background tasks, device features (camera, location), in-app purchases.</p></div></div>
          <div class="timeline-item"><div class="timeline-marker" aria-hidden="true"></div><div class="timeline-content"><span class="timeline-period">Months 15–18</span><h3>Architecture &amp; Portfolio</h3><p>Clean architecture, testing, CI/CD, performance optimization. Build 2–3 polished apps and publish to app stores.</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="tech-tags">
          <span class="tag">Swift</span><span class="tag">Kotlin</span><span class="tag">SwiftUI</span><span class="tag">Jetpack Compose</span><span class="tag">React Native</span><span class="tag">Flutter</span><span class="tag">Xcode</span><span class="tag">Android Studio</span><span class="tag">Firebase</span><span class="tag">REST APIs</span>
